## ðŸ§  Data Cleaning & Transformation (Python)
```python
import pandas as pd

# Load data
df = pd.read_csv('data/aws_cost_usage.csv')

# Drop duplicates and handle missing values
df.drop_duplicates(inplace=True)
df.fillna(0, inplace=True)

# Standardize column names
df.columns = df.columns.str.lower().str.replace(' ', '_')

# Convert cost columns to numeric
df['unblended_cost'] = pd.to_numeric(df['unblended_cost'], errors='coerce')

# Export cleaned data
df.to_csv('data/cleaned_cost_data.csv', index=False)
print("Data cleaned and ready for Snowflake upload.")
